Fail Fast  -> while iterating data is modified 
>> detects the changes in data structure early and throws concurrent modification exception >ex: HashMap
>> should use Iterator.remove() 

Fail safe -> while iterating data is modified 
>> no exception is thrown > uses Enumerations like in HashTable   hs.getKeys()  .hasMoreKeys();


HashMap (unsync k,V structure                              | Hash Table 
FailFast                                    Fail Safe
Fast                                             Slow 
Not thread safe- non sync (put,get)               Thread safe - synced ( 1 thread at a time 
Nulls allowed- 1 each side                     nulls not allowed

composed of:
K,V,Hash,NodeNxt                          :K,V,Entry<> 
modCount
